WEBVTT

00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:03.576
Ovo je slika sumraka na Marsu,

00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:07.080
koju je 2013. uslikala
svemirska letjelica NASA-e.

00:00:07.960 --> 00:00:09.816
Mars je jako hladan planet,

00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:12.096
ima visoke razine UV-zračenja

00:00:12.120 --> 00:00:14.016
te je iznimno suh.

00:00:14.040 --> 00:00:18.160
Zapravo, Mars je presuh
za život na kakav smo navikli.

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:20.176
Ja sam astrobiolog.

00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:23.096
Pokušavam razumjeti
podrijetlo života na Zemlji

00:00:23.120 --> 00:00:25.336
i mogućnosti pronalaska života

00:00:25.360 --> 00:00:26.600
drugdje u svemiru.

00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:28.656
Ljudi me nekad pitaju

00:00:28.680 --> 00:00:30.856
kako mogu biti astrobiolog